{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_41","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/bash -lc \"sed -n '1,260p' PR_COMMENTS.md\"","aggregated_output":"This change resolves the misclassification described in issue #3475.\n\nI updated `UBERON:0000961` by renaming it from `thoracic ganglion` to `thoracic paravertebral ganglion`. The term’s logical definition already modeled it as a paravertebral ganglion that is part of the thoracic sympathetic trunk, so the previous primary label was broader than the actual meaning of the class. I removed the auto-generated exact synonyms `ganglion of thorax` and `thorax ganglion`, and I retained the broader wording only as a `RELATED` synonym (`thoracic ganglion`).\n\nI also updated `UBERON:0002835` (`thoracic dorsal root ganglion`) by removing its asserted `is_a: UBERON:0000961` parentage. That restores consistency with the existing regional dorsal root ganglion pattern already used for cervical, lumbar, and sacral dorsal root ganglion classes, where the class is defined by genus-differentia rather than as a subclass of a sympathetic/paravertebral ganglion term.\n\nChecklist completed:\n- Read the imported issue context from `__issue_context__.json`\n- Inspected `UBERON:0000961` and `UBERON:0002835` in `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo`\n- Checked related parent/pattern consistency against other regional dorsal root ganglion classes\n- Edited via `obo-checkout.pl` / `obo-checkin.pl`\n- Reserialized `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo` with `robot convert -i src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo -f obo -o src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo`\n- Confirmed the conversion completed successfully\n\nCommitted locally as:\n- `2f63a11` `Fix thoracic ganglion classification for issue #3475`\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_42","type":"agent_message","text":"Updated `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo` to address issue `#3475` and committed it locally as `2f63a11`.\n\nThe change does two things: `UBERON:0000961` is now named `thoracic paravertebral ganglion`, and `UBERON:0002835` no longer inherits from that sympathetic/paravertebral class. I also removed the misleading auto-generated exact synonyms from `UBERON:0000961` and kept `thoracic ganglion` only as a `RELATED` synonym.\n\nValidation completed with `robot convert -i src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo -f obo -o src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo`.\n\nI also created uncommitted `ISSUE_COMMENTS.md` and `PR_COMMENTS.md` as requested."}}
